{
  "stem": "5388.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then somebody came and said, the Germans were-- the police, or the Germans came into Raczki.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were there just for three hours and moved out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So then around September 6, I went back to Raczki.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was already interested to see the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Let's see how they look.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What-- what is it all about?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they came in, and the first they came wasn't even military.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was the gendarmes with the brown [INAUDIBLE] and the white ones.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Jewish boys were running there to see, tried to talk to them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, everybody thinking, after all, he knows Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he knows German, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So-- and me among them, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Me among them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we-- but-- and then the Germans-- The Germans had been there in World War I?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, that's right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The people that knew the Germans-- that-- was nice, and gentlemen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You-- as a matter of fact, one of the great honors of-- of Raczki, what they had, was a picture of-- just a second-- either Hindenburg or Ludendorff-- I think it's Hindenburg, taking a piss right in the square of the town next to the car that they were chauffeuring him.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was a big honor that the city got from him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Urinating right in the center of the-- of the town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was passing it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Passed it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You better keep in mind, in 1915, you know, there was this big push of the Russian into Eastern Prussia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they were move-- pushed out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so he must have been there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyway.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
